org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.parsing

Class SourceFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.parsing.SourceFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISourceFragment

    public class SourceFragment
extends Object
implements ISourceFragment
    This class is an implementation of the ISourceFragment interface. It also adds the ability to split a fragment at a list of character indices within the logical text.
